summary: As a DCM analyst, I am involved across origination efforts, structuring, financial modelling, diligence, and transaction marketing, servicing both corporate clients on the issuer side and institutional clients on the investor side. Experience includes plain vanilla transactions as well as structured financings, from high yield bonds to project finance loans, across both senior as well as subordinated and mezzanine corporate debt mandates in Europe.
